window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Days from civilisation five men are about to experience something beyond the rational. </p> <p>In the snow slaked wilds where the natives fear to tread, these men search for moose but find something more terrifying and supernatural. With a rush of wind and the smell of feral nature one of their number is whisked away, leaving them wondering: Who might be next?</p>"; 
